[121.918904, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3Gisn't\u001b[9GLinux;\u001b[16GRoCE\u001b[21Gdies\u001b[26Gif\u001b[29Gwe\u001b[32Gcan't\u001b[38Gput\u001b[42Gan\u001b[45GRNIC\u001b[50Gin\u001b[53Git.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B2.\u001b[6G\u001b[1mCan the devstation get a dedicated point-to-point cable to clyffy-01\u001b[75G\u001b[22m(its\r\u001b[1B  own broadcast domain — one cable, no switch)? That solves the\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B  same-broadcast-domain constraint \u001b[3mand\u001b[23m most of the on-wire security question at\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B  once (physical link, MACsec or app-layer AEAD optional rather than mandatory).\r\u001b[1B  3. \u001b[1mWhat does ingestion actually carry and at what rate?\u001b[22m Notes corpora, file\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B  blobs, event streams, embeddings? \"Embedded fast\" as a target number — are we\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bchasing\u001b[11Gthroughput\u001b[22G(GB/s\u001b[28Gbulk\u001b[33Gingest)\u001b[41Gor\u001b[44Glatency\u001b[52G(µs\u001b[56Gper\u001b[60Gevent)?\u001b[68GB\u001b[70Gand\u001b[74GC\r\u001b[1B \u001b[3Goptimize diff\u001b[17Grent ends\u001b[27Gof that.\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BAnswer those three and I'll fire the research\u001b[49Gspurs\u001b[55G(2026\u001b[61Gstate\u001b[67Gof\u001b[70GAF_XDP\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bzero-copy\u001b[13G+\u001b[15Gio_uring,\u001b[25Gand\u001b[29GL2\u001b[32Gsecurity\u001b[41Goptions\u001b[49GMACsec-vs-AEAD)\u001b[65Gtargeted\u001b[74Gat\u001b[77Gthe\r\u001b[1B \u001b[3Gsurviving candidates instead of the whole field.\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m✻\u001b[3GSautéed for 1m 25s\r\u001b[4B\u001b[39m❯ \u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
[124.840132, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bisn't Linux; RoCE dies if we can't put an RNIC in it.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B2. \u001b[1mCan the devstation get a dedicated point-to-point cable to clyffy-01\u001b[75G\u001b[22m(its\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bown broadcast domain — \u001b[28Ge c\u001b[32Gble, no\u001b[40Gswi\u001b[44Gch)? That solv\u001b[59Gs the\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsam\u001b[7G-broadcast-domain constraint \u001b[3mand\u001b[23m most of the on-wire security question at\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bonce (physical link, MACsec or app-layer AEAD optional rath\u001b[63Gr\u001b[65Gthan m\u001b[72Gndatory).\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B3. \u001b[1mWhat does ingestion actually carry and at what rate?\u001b[22m Not\u001b[63Gs\u001b[65Gcorpo\u001b[71Ga,\u001b[74Gfile\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bblobs, event streams, embeddings? \"Embedded fast\" a\u001b[56Ga targ\u001b[63Gt number —\u001b[74Gare\u001b[78Gwe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bchasing throughpu\u001b[22G(GB/s bulk ingest)\u001b[41Gor\u001b[44Glatency\u001b[52G(µs\u001b[56Gper\u001b[60Gevent)?\u001b[68GB\u001b[70Gand\u001b[74GC\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Boptimize\u001b[12Gdifferent\u001b[22Gends\u001b[27Gof\u001b[30Gthat.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BAnswer those three and I'll fire the research\u001b[49Gspurs (2026 state of AF_XDP\u001b[77G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bze\u001b[6Go-copy\u001b[13G+ io_uring, and L2\u001b[32Gsecurity \u001b[42Gptions MACsec-vs-AEAD)\u001b[65Gtargeted\u001b[74Gat\u001b[77Gthe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsurviving\u001b[13Gcandidates\u001b[24Ginstead\u001b[32Gof\u001b[35Gthe\u001b[39Gwhole\u001b[45Gfield.\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
[124.856257, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[48;5;237m\u001b[38;5;239m❯ BRANCH l2-transport — sub-topic: Read ~/.deepdive/dives/devpulse-l2-session/…\u001b[39m \r\u001b[26C\u001b[14B\u001b[38;5;231m Jump to bottom (ctrl+End) ↓ \u001b[39m\u001b[49m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
[124.864775, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bbox?), a\u001b[12Gd what NIC does it have? AF_XDP dies instantly\u001b[59Gif\u001b[62Gthe\u001b[66Gdevstation\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bisn't Linux; RoCE dies if we can't put an RNIC in it.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B2. \u001b[1mCan the devstation get a dedicated point-to-point cable to clyffy-01\u001b[75G\u001b[22m(its\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bown broadcast domain — \u001b[28Ge c\u001b[32Gble, no\u001b[40Gswi\u001b[44Gch)? That solv\u001b[59Gs the\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsam\u001b[7G-broadcast-domain constraint \u001b[3mand\u001b[23m most of the on-wire security question at\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bonce (physical link, MACsec or app-layer AEAD optional rath\u001b[63Gr\u001b[65Gthan m\u001b[72Gndatory).\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B3. \u001b[1mWhat does ingestion actually carry and at what rate?\u001b[22m Not\u001b[63Gs\u001b[65Gcorpo\u001b[71Ga,\u001b[74Gfile\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bblobs, event streams, embeddings? \"Embedded fast\" a\u001b[56Ga targ\u001b[63Gt number —\u001b[74Gare\u001b[78Gwe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bchasing throughpu\u001b[22G(GB/s bulk ingest)\u001b[41Gor\u001b[44Glatency\u001b[52G(µs\u001b[56Gper\u001b[60Gevent)?\u001b[68GB\u001b[70Gand\u001b[74GC\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Boptimize\u001b[12Gdifferent\u001b[22Gends\u001b[27Gof\u001b[30Gthat.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BAnswer those three and I'll fire the research\u001b[49Gspurs (2026 state of AF_XDP\u001b[77G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bze\u001b[6Go-copy\u001b[13G+ io_uring, and L2\u001b[32Gsecurity \u001b[42Gptions MACsec-vs-AEAD)\u001b[65Gtargeted\u001b[74Gat\u001b[77Gthe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsurviving\u001b[13Gcandidates\u001b[24Gins\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
