[334.596377, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[48;5;237m\u001b[38;5;239m❯ linux and windows and mac, we want to have a secure protocol like a vpn brid…\u001b[39m \r\u001b[26C\u001b[11B\u001b[38;5;231m Jump to bottom (ctrl+End) ↓ \u001b[39m\u001b[49m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[16;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
