[366.11918, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3Gcandidates\u001b[14Ghonestly: \u001b[1mLinux + Windows + Mac clients rules out \u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mAF_XDP/AF_PACKET/RoCE on the client side\u001b[22m (all Linux-only). What you're\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdescribing — \"a secure VPN-like bridge that builds itself seamlessly after\u001b[78Gthe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bea\u001b[6Gy HTTP connection\"\u001b[25G— is a \u001b[3msecure overlay bootstrapped from HTTP\u001b[23m,\u001b[71Gand\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bthere's\u001b[11Ga\u001b[13Ggenuinely\u001b[23Gcutting-edge\u001b[36G2026\u001b[41Gmenu\u001b[46Gfor\u001b[50Gexactly\u001b[58Gthat.\u001b[64GFiring\u001b[71Gtwo\r\u001b[1B \u001b[3Gresearch spurs i\u001b[20G the ba\u001b[28Gkground while we talk.\r\u001b[3C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;114m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39m\u001b[1m2\u001b[22m background agents launched \u001b[38;5;246m(↓ to manage)\r\u001b[3C\u001b[1B├\u001b[6G\u001b[39m\u001b[1mResearch MASQUE/QUIC tunnel state\r\u001b[1B\u001b[22m \u001b[3G \u001b[38;5;246m└\u001b[39m \u001b[1mResearch embedded WG + PQ + L2 overlays\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;211m✻\u001b[3GWaiting for API response\u001b[38;5;246m · will retry in 2m 40s · check your network\u001b[39m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[16;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
