[578.219643, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BDoes edge-te\u001b[16Gmination\u001b[25Gmatch your\u001b[36Gint\u001b[40Gnt, or do\u001b[50Gyou specifically want DevPulse\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bto be\u001b[9Ga citizen of the fabric's broadcast domain? And of the three bridge\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bflavors — boring-fast\u001b[25GWireGuard,\u001b[36Gbleeding-edge\u001b[50GMASQUE,\u001b[58Gor\u001b[61Gtrue-L2\u001b[69GZeroTier\u001b[78G—\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bwhich\u001b[9Gsmells\u001b[16Gright?\u001b[23G(The\u001b[28Gspurs\u001b[34Gwill\u001b[39Greport\u001b[46Gback\u001b[51Gwith\u001b[56Gmaturity\u001b[65Gverdicts\u001b[74Gto\r\u001b[1B \u001b[3Gcheck us either way.)\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;5;246m✻\u001b[3GWaiting for \u001b[1m2\u001b[22m background agents to finish\u001b[45G\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;5;114m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mAgent \"Research\u001b[19GMASQUE/QUIC\u001b[31Gtunnel\u001b[38Gstate\"\u001b[45Gfinished\u001b[38;5;246m · 4m 4s\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;174m·\u001b[3G\u001b[38;5;216mSwi\u001b[38;5;174mrling… \u001b[39m              \u001b[56G\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[16;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
[578.235934, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BD\u001b[5Ges edge-\u001b[14Germination match your intent, or do you specifically want DevPulse\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bto be a\u001b[11Gcitize\u001b[18G o\u001b[21G the fabric's broadcast domain? And of the three b\u001b[72Gidg\u001b[76G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bflavor\u001b[10G — borin\u001b[19G-fast WireG\u001b[31Gard, b\u001b[38Geeding-edge MASQUE, or true-L2 ZeroTier\u001b[78G—\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bw\u001b[5Gi\u001b[7Gh\u001b[9Gsmells right? (The\u001b[28Gspurs\u001b[34Gwill\u001b[39Greport\u001b[46Gback\u001b[51Gwith\u001b[56Gmaturity\u001b[65Gverdicts\u001b[74Gto\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcheck\u001b[9Gus\u001b[12Geither\u001b[19Gway.)\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m✻\u001b[3GWaiting for \u001b[1m2\u001b[22m background agents to finish\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;114m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mAgent\u001b[9G\"Research\u001b[19GMASQUE/QUIC\u001b[31Gtunnel\u001b[38Gstate\"\u001b[45Gfinished\u001b[38;5;246m · 4m 4s\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m \u001b[3G          \u001b[23;1H\u001b[16;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
[578.251007, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mingestion stream inside it\u001b[30G\u001b[22m—\u001b[32Gwith\u001b[37Glocal\u001b[43Gmode\u001b[48Ggoing\u001b[54Gdirect\u001b[61Gover\u001b[66Gthe\u001b[70GLAN\u001b[74Gand\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bnetworked mode traversing NAT/relay through\u001b[47Gthe same tunnel identity.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BDoes edge-te\u001b[16Gmination\u001b[25Gmatch your\u001b[36Gint\u001b[40Gnt, or do\u001b[50Gyou specifically want DevPulse\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bto be\u001b[9Ga citizen of the fabric's broadcast domain? And of the three bridge\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bflavors — boring-fast\u001b[25GWireGuard,\u001b[36Gbleeding-edge\u001b[50GMASQUE,\u001b[58Gor\u001b[61Gtrue-L2\u001b[69GZeroTier\u001b[78G—\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bwhich\u001b[9Gsmells\u001b[16Gright?\u001b[23G(The\u001b[28Gspurs\u001b[34Gwill\u001b[39Greport\u001b[46Gback\u001b[51Gwith\u001b[56Gmaturity\u001b[65Gverdicts\u001b[74Gto\r\u001b[1B \u001b[3Gcheck us either way.)\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;5;246m✻\u001b[3GWaiting for \u001b[1m2\u001b[22m background agents to finish\u001b[45G\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[16;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
[578.283453, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BSo the shape I think you're actual\u001b[38Gy describing is: \u001b[1mHTTP handshake → in-app \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsecure tunnel (pick 1, 2, or 3) → terminates at the cluster edge → rkyv-framed\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bingestion stream inside it\u001b[30G\u001b[22m—\u001b[32Gwith\u001b[37Glocal\u001b[43Gmode\u001b[48Ggoing\u001b[54Gdirect\u001b[61Gover\u001b[66Gthe\u001b[70GLAN\u001b[74Gand\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bnetworked mode traversing NAT/relay through\u001b[47Gthe same tunnel identity.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BDoes edge-te\u001b[16Gmination\u001b[25Gmatch your\u001b[36Gint\u001b[40Gnt, or do\u001b[50Gyou specifically want DevPulse\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bto be\u001b[9Ga citizen of the fabric's broadcast domain? And of the three bridge\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bflavors — boring-fast\u001b[25GWireGuard,\u001b[36Gbleeding-edge\u001b[50GMASQUE,\u001b[58Gor\u001b[61Gtrue-L2\u001b[69GZeroTier\u001b[78G—\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bwhich\u001b[9Gsmells\u001b[16Gright?\u001b[23G(The\u001b[28Gspurs\u001b[34Gwill\u001b[39Greport\u001b[46Gback\u001b[51Gwith\u001b[56Gmaturity\u001b[65Gverdicts\u001b[74Gto\r\u001b[1B \u001b[3Gcheck us either way.)\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[16;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
