[705.003283, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G(killed by cross-platform clients) and literal L2 b\u001b[55Gidg\u001b[59Gng (killed\u001b[70Gon security\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bgrounds).\u001b[13GZ\u001b[15GroTie\u001b[21G rejected on licensing + weight. No\u001b[57Ghing\u001b[62Gprior in the dive\u001b[K\r\u001b[3C\u001b[1Bs\u001b[6Gover\u001b[11Gurne\u001b[16G.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BIf\u001b[6Gthis\u001b[11Gmatches\u001b[19Gyour\u001b[24Gintent,\u001b[32Ggive\u001b[37Gme\u001b[40Gyour\u001b[45G\"yes\u001b[50G+\u001b[52Gwhy\"\u001b[57Gin\u001b[60Gyour\u001b[65Gown\u001b[69Gwords\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(that's what goes in the decision notes verbatim), and I'll write the\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BDECISIONS.md section + build no\u001b[35Ges\u001b[42Gwe close the branch. Push back\u001b[73Ganywhere\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bit doe\u001b[10Gn't sit right — especial\u001b[35Gy if you\u001b[44Gtruly wanted fabric-level L2\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcitiz\u001b[9Gnship, because\u001b[24GI'm\u001b[28Gexplicitly\u001b[39Grecommending\u001b[52Gagainst\u001b[60Gthat.\r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;5;174m✻\u001b[3G\u001b[38;5;216mZig\u001b[38;5;174mzagging… \u001b[38;5;246m(43s · ↓\u001b[24G1.8k tokens)\u001b[37G\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m  ⎿  Tip: Use /btw to ask a quick side question without interrupting Claude's \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m   \u001b[38;5;246mcurrent work\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;4H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
