[705.176777, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BIf thi\u001b[10G matches you\u001b[23G intent, give me your \"y\u001b[48Gs + why\" in you\u001b[64G \u001b[66Gwn words\u001b[75G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(that's what goes\u001b[21Gin\u001b[24Gthe\u001b[28Gdecision\u001b[37Gnotes\u001b[43Gverbatim),\u001b[54Gand\u001b[58GI'll\u001b[63Gwrite\u001b[69Gthe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BDECISIONS.md\u001b[16Gsection\u001b[24G+\u001b[26Gbuild\u001b[32Gnotes\u001b[38Gand\u001b[42Gwe\u001b[45Gclose\u001b[51Gthe\u001b[55Gbranch.\u001b[63GPush\u001b[68Gback\u001b[73Ganywhere\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bit\u001b[6Gdoe\u001b[10Gn't sit right\u001b[24G— especially\u001b[37Gif\u001b[43G truly\u001b[50Gwanted\u001b[57Gfabric-level L2\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcitizenship,\u001b[16Gbecause\u001b[24GI'm\u001b[28Gexplicitly r\u001b[41Gcommending ag\u001b[55Ginst that.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m✻\u001b[3GCogitated for 7m 10s\u001b[24G\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m  ⎿  Tip: Use /btw to ask a quick side question without interrupting Claude's \r\u001b[1B\u001b[48;5;237m\u001b[38;5;239m❯ \u001b[38;5;231mEdge termination\u001b[39m                                                              \r\u001b[1B\u001b[49m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;174m✽\u001b[39m \u001b[38;5;174mGallivanting… \u001b[38;5;246m(0s ·\u001b[23G↓\u001b[39m \u001b[38;5;246m1.8k token\u001b[36G)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m  ⎿  Tip: Dynamic workflows let Claude write a script that orchestrates many \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1Bagents for you. Mention the keyword \u001b[38;5;153multracode\u001b[38;5;246m or ask Claude to use a \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m   \u001b[38;5;246mworkflow directly.\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;4H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
