[729.065135, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3GIf this matches your\u001b[24Gintent,\u001b[32Ggiv\u001b[36G me your\u001b[45G\"ye\u001b[49G + why\" i\u001b[59G your own words\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(\u001b[5Ghat'\u001b[10G what goes in\u001b[24Gth\u001b[27G d\u001b[32Gsion\u001b[37Gnotes ve\u001b[46Gbatim), and I'll writ\u001b[68G the\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BDECISIONS.md\u001b[16Gs\u001b[19Gtion\u001b[24G+ build notes and we close the branch. Push\u001b[68Gback\u001b[73Ganywhere\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bit\u001b[6Gdoesn't\u001b[14Gsit\u001b[18Gright\u001b[24G—\u001b[26Gespecially\u001b[37Gif\u001b[40Gyou\u001b[44Gtruly\u001b[50Gwanted\u001b[57Gfabric-level\u001b[70GL2\r\u001b[1B \u001b[3Gcitizenship, because\u001b[24GI'm\u001b[28Gexplicitly\u001b[39Grecommending\u001b[52Gagainst\u001b[60Gthat.\r\u001b[2B\u001b[38;5;246m✻\u001b[39m \u001b[38;5;246mCogitated for 7m 10s\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2B\u001b[48;5;237m\u001b[38;5;239m❯ \u001b[38;5;231mEdge termination\u001b[39m                                                              \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[49m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mLocked:\u001b[11G\u001b[1medge termination\u001b[28G\u001b[22m—\u001b[30Gthe\u001b[34GDAC\u001b[38Gfabric\u001b[45Gstays\u001b[51Gsealed,\u001b[59Gthe\u001b[63Gbridge\u001b[70Glands\u001b[76Gon\r\u001b[1B \u001b[3Gclyffy-01's LAN face, and that goes in the notes as your\u001b[60Gcall\u001b[65Gwith\u001b[70Gyour\u001b[75Gstated\r\u001b[1B  reason (protecting the GB10 cluster fabric is \u001b[3mwhy\u001b[23m the bridge exists at all).\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BOne final confirm before\u001b[28GI\u001b[30Gwrite\u001b[36Gthe\u001b[40Gclose-out,\u001b[51Gbecause\u001b[59Git's\u001b[64Gthe\u001b[68Gother\u001b[74Ghalf\u001b[79Gof\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;4H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
