[1010.522634, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3Grkyv→FlatBuffers supersession), \u001b[1myour reasoning in your own words\u001b[22m, the research\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bgrounding from both spurs, and build-plan notes for the fold — including\u001b[76Gthe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bopen handoff to branch 2: \u001b[3ma session must survive a dead QUIC connection, not \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bjust a migrated one.\u001b[23m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B-\u001b[5G\u001b[38;5;153m\u001b[1mSUMMARY.md\u001b[22m\u001b[39m — l2-transport flipped OPEN→CLOSED with the 3-line decision\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsummary\u001b[11G+\u001b[13Gbuild\u001b[19Gnotes.\r\u001b[1B \u001b[3G- \u001b[1mFold signal\u001b[22m —\u001b[19G\u001b[38;5;153mcrystallized\u001b[32G\u001b[39mqueued\u001b[39Gfor\u001b[43Gl2-transport\u001b[56G(queue\u001b[63Gfallback\u001b[72Gagain;\r\u001b[1B  reminder from earlier: \u001b[38;5;153mclyffy signal fold\u001b[39m cold-loads the 138 GB model and\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BCUDA-crashes — worth a fix, logged, not this branch's business).\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mExit this session now (Ctrl+C twice or \u001b[38;5;153m/exit\u001b[39m) — that exit auto-triggers branch\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B2: session-ownership\u001b[22m,\u001b[25Gwhere\u001b[31Gwe\u001b[34Gdesign\u001b[41Gthe\u001b[45Gclyffy-owned\u001b[58Gneutral-space\u001b[72Gsession\r\u001b[1B \u001b[3Gmodel that picks up exactly where this decision\u001b[51Gleft\u001b[56Goff.\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m✻\u001b[3GChurned for 1m 13s\r\u001b[4B\u001b[39m❯ \u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
