[1169.744407, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3Gfallback), th\u001b[17G killed cand\u001b[30Gdates named one by one (including the mid-b\u001b[74Ganch\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Brkyv→FlatBuffers superse\u001b[28Gsio\u001b[32G), \u001b[1myour reasoning in your own words\u001b[22m, the research\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bgroundi\u001b[11Gg \u001b[14Grom both spurs, and build-plan notes for the fold — including the\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bopen handoff to branch\u001b[26G2:\u001b[29G\u001b[3ma session must survive a dead QUIC connection, not \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bjust a migrated one.\u001b[23m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[38;5;153m\u001b[1mSUMMARY.md\u001b[22m\u001b[39m — l2-\u001b[22Gransport\u001b[31Gflipped\u001b[39GOPEN→CLOSED\u001b[51Gwith\u001b[56Gthe\u001b[60G3-line\u001b[67Gdecision\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsummary + build\u001b[19Gnotes.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mFold signal\u001b[17G\u001b[22m— \u001b[38;5;153mcrystallized\u001b[39m queued for l2-transport\u001b[56G(queue fallback again;\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Breminder from earlier:\u001b[26G\u001b[38;5;153mclyffy signal fold\u001b[39m cold-loads the 138 GB model\u001b[73Gand\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BCUDA-crashes\u001b[16G—\u001b[18Gworth\u001b[24Ga\u001b[26Gfix,\u001b[31Glogged,\u001b[39Gnot\u001b[43Gthis\u001b[48Gbranch's\u001b[57Gbusiness).\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mExit th\u001b[11Gs session now (Ctrl+C twice or \u001b[38;5;153m/exit\u001b[39m) — that exit auto-triggers branch\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B2: session-ownership\u001b[22m, where\u001b[32Ge d\u001b[36Gsign th\u001b[44G clyffy-owned neutral-space\u001b[72Gsession\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bmodel\u001b[9Gthat\u001b[14Gpicks\u001b[20Gup\u001b[23Gexactly\u001b[31Gwhere\u001b[37Gthis\u001b[42Gdecision\u001b[51Gleft\u001b[56Goff.\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m✻\u001b[3GChurned for 1m 13s\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[48;5;37m\u001b[38;5;16m dd:Read ~/.d\u001b[15Gepdive/dives/devpulse-l2-session/bri